{"type": "article", "id": 26544, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-09T06:56:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27328, "name": "Secretello desk"}, {"id": 27329, "name": "Waterscapes"}, {"id": 27330, "name": "Minko Buds"}, {"id": 27331, "name": "Chair Sylph"}, {"id": 27332, "name": "Aro lamp"}, {"id": 27333, "name": "Jordi Blasi"}, {"id": 27334, "name": "ONEMI Radio"}, {"id": 27335, "name": "Michele de Lucchi"}, {"id": 27336, "name": "Minko"}, {"id": 27337, "name": "大舍建筑"}, {"id": 27338, "name": "Shackleton Group"}, {"id": 27339, "name": "三澤遥"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031213588yXruW0xCYPQ6SOM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Secretello desk by Michele de Lucchi</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.amdl.it/\">Michele de Lucchi</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.molteni.it/en/\" target=\"_blank\">Molteni&amp;C</a> 设计的这款名为 Secretello 的桌子很容易让人想起图书馆内那些隔开的自习空间。安全玻璃罩的设计则为经典的造型增添了新意，看上去既是一个实用的工作桌，也是一个很有现代感的展示橱窗，能够表达使用者的个性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181122yptSzf5QAeoD0nZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88753056\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071811231aqfTkUBhdgF2HNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88875306\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181123Wpnwd3M2OQTkxqtN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88753056\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181123ZOv2zEaHyXLQekwP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181124lnzxmjs9IWMF8LRi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32640587\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181125d0HrFQef18v5hsaY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Waterscapes by <b>三澤遥</b>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"\">日本设计师<a href=\"http://misawa.ndc.co.jp/\">三澤遥</a>最近设计的 Waterscapes 系列鱼缸，是不是名副其实的“鱼住的水景房”？四四方方的透明鱼缸中放有各种奇异的造型物，以一种独特的方式模拟了水下的环境，而且都非常美观。不过，目前这些鱼缸还处于雏形阶段，三澤遥在她的<a href=\"http://www.kingstone.com.tw/book/book_page.asp?kmcode=2019600052539\">新书</a>中公开了作品的细节。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181125yq67xjRYlkIBQKSn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181126i9Svn1yIoG7NgdXT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181126olQ58nEIjFqZNO3m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071811268ULOB1GXnxch9NKq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181127b2COQTR4c5kvVKEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181127YCTloh1Xgc3axdsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Minko Buds by Minko</h2>\n<p class=\"\">要说到那些让人心烦意乱的小事，耳机线绕得像麻花一定是其中一件，而这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.minkobuds.com/\">Minko Buds</a> 的收纳工具可以让你省心不少。它由三个可以拆开的零件组成，每一个零件都单独“负责”耳机线的一部分，完全不妨碍你使用它听音乐，收纳时只要把三个零件拼在一起就大功告成了。Minko Buds 在<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Minko-Buds-Untangle-your-earphones/dp/B01DJVEGNS\">亚马逊</a>上有售，价格为 9.99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181128YFbNB4DIRqz1fUZ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181128j5tVhcPXLdEIus7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181129jMbrHPUDYG4oAzxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071811298nOCHV6MmGa7gRUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181130zr0o1a56TyO9B2AD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071811307g6kQTdzIqJO3hGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>窈窕淑椅 by 大舍建筑</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这一系列利用了木材与圆钢的椅子有一个非常形象的名字叫“窈窕淑椅”，由<a href=\"http://www.deshaus.com/\">大舍建筑设计事务所</a>设计。一根完整的圆钢经过弯曲后组成了把手、椅背和后腿，而圆形且微微弯曲的座椅和前腿则由木材这一传统的家具材料所制成。两者组合后形成了一种鲜明的反差，看似纤细但并不脆弱。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181131wK2XU0EjINbHkPOC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181131BRAdFWNVLozMyfbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181132zpORYANQ7BMJ2xfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37604167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181132mS1XWQV2Lu3asMkD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181133z1I6xUE9TidySona.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Aro lamp by Jordi Blasi</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.jordiblasi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Jordi Blasi</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.estiluz.com/en/colecciones/aro\">Aro</a> 是一个极简风格的黑色灯具，可以根据需要自由调节。它的主体为圆盘形，通过背面的小圆环不仅能够灵活地上下移动、左右旋转，也能同其他类型的灯柱匹配在一起，变成一盏落地灯或是台灯。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071811337jGba6CTKM3em10k.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7152381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181133yBAU8htQ7WOfjVMr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181134oAeFp7S60EsUvLnR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.30380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181134K8eX4mgUS9COozBi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071811352l4XcTtERiZIYgUp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181135rE8kVpYfGz5lbcAo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>ONEMI Radio by Shackleton Group</h2>\n<p class=\"\">要说到能为社会带来帮助的好设计，<a href=\"http://www.shackletongroup.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Shackleton Group</a> 为智利的国家紧急情况办公室 ONEMI 设计的这款纸板型收音机就是其中的典范。作为一个地震多发的国家，这款收音机可以让民众在发生紧急情况时收听到消息。选用纸板这一材质不仅便于发放和携带，组装也比较容易。纸板的一面还装有一块太阳能板，用来为收音机提供电力。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181136Bw25y83inNVGq1ID.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071811369lRCUuEgq2fdBM3b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181137mT0SAaLsF6ehRkD5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181137rTNvPYmk6u8KCbzy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181138CqbmVvs0Gh8rTnyl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}